%e A394327 1274 is in this sequence because d(1274) = 12, d(1275) = 12, and d(1276) = 12, so the minimum value is 12. And there is no number k < 1274 where min(d(k), d(k+1), d(k+2)) >= 12.
%o A394327 (PARI) print1(r=1); for(n=2, 1e5, if(min(min(numdiv(n), numdiv(n+1)), numdiv(n+2))>r, r=min(min(numdiv(n), numdiv(n+1)), numdiv(n+2)); print1(", "n)))
